---
# var-naming[no-role-prefix] wants every variable renamed with a role prefix
# (mc_version -> minecraft_version, etc.). With only two roles and no actual
# naming collisions, that's a repo-wide rename for a purely cosmetic
# namespacing concern - not worth the churn or the re-verification effort
# for a project this size.
skip_list:
  - var-naming[no-role-prefix]
